<h1>Learn</h1>

<p>
  DJ education for Zouk DJs at all levels — from the fundamentals of music structure to advanced transition techniques.
</p>

<h2>The Loop Academy</h2>
<p>
  The Loop Academy is a year-long program taking students from complete beginner to working DJ, run through
  <a href="https://theloop.community" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Loop</a> — a community for Zouk DJs.
</p>
<p>
  The program covers everything from music theory and equipment basics to set building, energy management, and
  performing at real events. It is taught by three working Zouk DJs from across the globe:
</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="/">DJ Sprenk</a> — USA</li>
  <li><a href="https://linktr.ee/djkron" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DJ Kron</a> — Czech Republic</li>
  <li><a href="https://www.djxearo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DJ Xearo</a> — The Netherlands</li>
</ul>
<p>
  <a href="https://theloop.community" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Learn more at theloop.community →</a>
</p>

<h2>Private Lessons</h2>
<p>
  One-on-one instruction tailored to where you are and where you want to go — whether you're just starting out or
  refining your craft.
  <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a> to set something up.
</p>

